        Parameters:
        ssdBrand - ssd producer
        ssdSerialNumber - producer serial number code
        ssdName - producer name
        ssdInterfaceType - interface type
        ssdFormFactor - form factor
        ssdProtocol - protocol name [AHCI, NVME 1.4, ...]
        ssdCapacity - capacity [GB]
        ssdReadSpeed - read speed [MB/s]
        ssdWriteSpeed - write speed [MB/s]
        ssdMemoryType - memory type [SLC/MLC/TLC]
        ssdTbw - tbw-factor (TeraBytes written)
        ssdControllerManufacturer - controller manufacturer
        ssdControllerModel - controller model name
        ssdWattage - wattage which is used to calculate PSU requirements [W]
        ssdhasRadiator - does this ssd has a radiator?
        ssdPrice - ssd price
        ssdImagePath - path to big image file
        ssdSmallImagePath - path to small image file
